OL,3,CPolice on e-bikes in Cornwall and
OL,4,CDevon to boost neighbourhood engagement
OL,6,FFollowing a successful pilot of e-
OL,7,Fbikes, Devon and Cornwall Police have
OL,8,Fnow rolled out the scheme to other
OL,9,Fareas to boost neighbourhood
OL,10,Fengagement.
OL,12,FThe pilot was initially launched in
OL,13,FCornwall and supported by Cornwall
OL,14,FCouncil.
OL,16,FThere are now 39 e-bikes in use across
OL,17,FCamborne, Plymouth, Penzance, Exeter,
OL,18,FBodmin, Cullompton, Falmouth, Truro
OL,19,FLaunceston, Hayle and Helston.
