OL,3,CPolice on e-bikes in Cornwall and
OL,4,CDevon to boost neighbourhood engagement
OL,6,FIn one day, an officer covered 71km
OL,7,Fusing an e-bike and received positive
OL,8,Ffeedback from the community.
OL,10,FWork is underway to purchase more e-
OL,11,Fbikes and deploy them to more sites
OL,12,Faround Devon and Cornwall.
OL,14,FSuperintendent Ian Thompson said: "The
OL,15,Felectric bikes initiative is boosting
OL,16,Fthe ability of our neighbourhood teams
OL,17,Fto engage with and be visible in their
OL,18,Fcommunities, whilst allowing them to
OL,19,Fbe in places that do not always have a
OL,20,Fpolice presence.
