OL,3,CPolice on e-bikes in Cornwall and
OL,4,CDevon to boost neighbourhood engagement
OL,6,F"In turn, this is taking the pressure
OL,7,Foff our vehicle fleet and allowing us
OL,8,Fto be less reliant on cars and reduce
OL,9,Four carbon footprint.
OL,11,F"The feedback from officers is
OL,12,Fextremely positive, who realise the
OL,13,Fbenefits of faster, quieter patrols
OL,14,Fand the wellbeing benefits of being
OL,15,Factive and outside.
